
Ranger Help for: port
=====================

SUMMARY:    
Ports are areas where ships dock and are stored when not in use. Ports
or docks are humanoid-made, usually of wood. They are almost always
wet with pieces of dead fish laying around. They are no place for
some of nature, like a Ranger is. Skills are somewhat limited on
ports, and no Rangers live on or near them. Ports can be found on
all of the continents.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

